snippet.title: Ranch Mayhem Trailer
snippet.description:
Ranch Mayhem is an active idle game. Explore 15 crops, face invasions, and spend them for bonuses. Enjoy the changing seasons and the farming adventure at your own pace. 

Wishlist the game on Steam now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2818590/Ranch_Mayhem__Active_Idler/
